==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*στίγμα / stigma / stig'-mah
*From a primary word [[στίζω]] stizō (to “stick”, that is, prick); a mark incised or punched (for recognition of ownership), that is, (figuratively) scar of service:

===Noun===
'''στίγμα'''

# A [[mark]].

